{"type": "article", "id": 7939, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-03-31T08:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2209, "name": "餐具"}, {"id": 1327, "name": "雨伞"}, {"id": 8387, "name": "军刀"}, {"id": 8388, "name": "荧光粉"}], "category": 17, "column": null, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061428293T5lEruVoOBiwq8a.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tClassic Wood Grain Keychain Army Knife by Sneaker Politics \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t球鞋品牌 Sneaker Politics 推出了一款自己家的木纹钥匙扣军刀。刀柄采用纯天然的木材，表面雕刻着 “Politics” 的标记。内部配备有剪刀和另外两种刀具。原本冷冰的刀具搭配温暖的木材，给人以更加亲切和新鲜的感觉。这款产品目前售价为 10 美元，这里是<a href=\"http://sneakerpolitics.com/collections/new/products/sneaker-politics-classic-keychain-army-knife-wood-grain\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142813JcTqeazsivXDo1tM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142814eycukTlGw6DdAPIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142814YlLm5nUjk714QgZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142815bTd2VkPDtCXsp6qj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLife Paint by Volvo \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t在英国，每年有 19000 人因为骑自行车受伤。Volvo 近来推出了一款喷涂材料，用于提高夜间骑行者的“可见度”和安全性。这里的“可见度”不是骑行者本人能看见什么，而是别人多大程度上能看见骑行者。当骑行者在夜间骑车的时候，可以在自己身上，车上喷上 Life Paint，在黑暗中仍然是黑色，但只有有车灯照到涂料的喷涂区域，涂料就会发出荧光，告诉司机前面有人。涂料的作用可以持续 10 天，但是很容易被洗净。目前这款产品正在英国伦敦和肯特郡地区试推行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061428159jsG6KFH84TOJPvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42521368\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142816QGzw8nAE4S3sVPdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142816wzc34CJt1A7MxNXn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42521368\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142817lbm5j0J3SRQWHO9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42521368\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142817KRFf0Pcay7q4pJnX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42521368\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142818vthdaNAIq6pYJTmZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tFocus by Zilenzio\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t现代人对于隐私的要求无处不在，Focus 正是针对此需求而设计的。这是一个桌面分隔屏，把它放在桌子上，便可以划出一个暂时的私人区域。折叠式的设计使得它十分便于携带，对于咖啡厅，图书馆等去处，看起来都是蛮不错的选择。这款产品有两种尺寸，一种适于单人，而另一种长款可以绕过更大的桌子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142818xG7d0VYAgOk5UqzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142819IS4AlNvtnUwRPpYF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614281913B2IT0gcdHxFRCi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061428202JXL84vRizWSQHku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142820ymp6Wn2a71s5FgBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tWet-Free Unnurella Umbrella by Kazuya Koike \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t设计师 Kazuya Koike 设计了一款不沾水的雨伞，用来解决雨伞遇水后会有水柱流下，即使收起来也会打湿地板，或难以带在身上等问题。这款雨伞的伞面采用的是特殊的高密度织物材料，遇到水只需要轻轻一抖，水珠便会悉数落下，不留痕迹，便于携带。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142821S3IA6jE2bHOrUdVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142821cq6ReHDXzCuGtgZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142821SckrKuo8YhmOgts4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142822KjUWlw7tm9JHRrZB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142823YTdUvSMQCPkxLhHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142823gN71CRlqW0dQ2eKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60146699\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142824NLZResTuG4SWqfg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142824QOtNr98pcKiXY1yn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tGlop by Berta Julià Sala\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t西班牙设计师 Berta Julià Sala 的这套作品由 5 个食物容器组成，特别的是，这些容器可以被“捏”成任何一样东西的样子，杯子，罐子，碟子，碗等等。举个例子来说，我们用大碗洗完水果，只需要捏住碗口，就可以在食物不落下来的情况下把水倒干——相信现在大部分人的做法是用手挡住吧。他们甚至还能被封住口，作为存储空间使用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142825vcyfrgUTR7t4wpBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142825gNSWLxq8G1KXOsPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142825PcYuAr637ZDUMsd1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142826LCh3sKwZz9H0u6Mi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142826iCvEn2Dw8t4uM7dq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142827I5FBpRxNtf1WKUCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18704156\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142827TUNGEI5Hp6ukBqf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78728606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142828rZ7G4k5LC0znAIdt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061428285N0ix2GIWZDmlk9M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7408313\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}